--------------------

add_gold - Adds gold to a character, in a scripted (i.e. NOT hard-coded) manner
Supported Scopes: character

--------------------

set_relation - Sets a scripted relation between the scoped character and the target
The relation name comes from the scripted relations database.
Supported Scopes: character
Supported Targets: character

--------------------

trigger_event - Triggers the specified event for the current scope
Requires Data: yes
Supported Scopes: none/all

--------------------

remove_trait - Removes a trait from a character
Supported Scopes: character
